      "module_path": "tddd",
      "docs": "Secondary port that loads all per-layer rustdoc baselines for a given track as a Vec<BaselineDocument>. Each BaselineDocument carries its own LayerId so callers can group by layer without additional context. Symmetric to CatalogueLoader (which loads CatalogueDocument per layer). Implementations discover tddd.enabled layers via architecture-rules.json and load the associated rustdoc JSON for each layer. (IN-02 / IN-19 / AC-02 / CN-03)",
